quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,"When the earth will be shaken with a mighty shaking,",footnotes:182808:1
  99,2,"and the earth will throw up all her burdens,",footnotes:182809:1
  99,3,"and man will cry out: “What is the matter with her?”",footnotes:182810:1
  99,4,"On that Day it will relate all her news,",footnotes:182811:1
  99,5,"for your Lord will have commanded her (to do so)."
  99,6,"On that Day people will go forth in varying states so that they be shown their deeds.",footnotes:182812:1|182813:2
  99,7,"So, whoever does an atom's weight of good shall see it;"
  99,8,"and whoever does an atom's weight of evil shall see it.",footnotes:182814:1
